{"tid":2268786,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"法庭：警員供詞矛盾奇怪　被控堵路中六生脫罪","createTime":"2020-11-03T05:14:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-03T05:41:49.000Z","uid":20933,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8daaba3f9959b3004decccc21b6b3710b7a3d228","tid":2268786,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T05:14:49.000Z","msg":"一名19歲中六生去年11月涉嫌在西灣河堵路，被控一項在公眾地方造成阻礙罪，案件在東區裁判法院審理。裁判官認為警員的供詞矛盾奇怪，不接納其供詞，裁定被告罪名不成立。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官黃雅茵認為，警員的供詞出現多次出入，有不同說法。她又認為相比黑衣及灰褲等，被告鄧楚豐當時較明顯的特徵是携帶黑色背囊，但警員未在第一次書面供詞或記事冊中提及，反而在庭上作供時突然提及，令人懷疑警員事後才發現被告帶有背囊。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官又表示，被告自辯時未說出全部真相，但由於警員的口供未能證實被告就是他所看見的堵路男子，因此裁定被告無罪。"},{"pid":"e8b8a8aca94a2d36635cb4fcb9693b726c9be9d7","tid":2268786,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T05:14:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1558083-20201103.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1558083-20201103.htm&d=tGWxp70K68wBh01xS7f0EswCZVYJieBIKSEfzXA%2FSmA%3D&h=d6771253\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1558083-20201103.htm&h=e83db1b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1558083-20201103.htm</a>"},{"pid":"9d8a9e56deb61205b1d8ede346ed256b9f007a23","tid":2268786,"uid":148315,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T05:38:45.000Z","msg":"又一單blackbloc重要性<br />\n雖然唔black得晒<br />\n但好過着彩虹戰衣落場"},{"pid":"aed66e7ea2006fb67ee2fc9c8b0bd1414e4abaf0","tid":2268786,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T05:39:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ce5eb7af82da712a8b242c346679d3ad06a53f7","tid":2268786,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T05:41:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img s